* Table History &\nVersion Changes
** Catalog Explorer
***_ History tab on Delta tables
***_ Version, timestamp, operation, user
** SQL command
***_ DESCRIBE HISTORY <table>
***_ LIMIT N for recent history
** History columns
***_ version: table version number
***_ timestamp: when operation occurred
***_ operation: WRITE, UPDATE, DELETE, MERGE
***_ userName: who made the change
***_ operationMetrics: rows affected, files
** Use cases
***_ Auditing and compliance
***_ Point-in-time recovery
***_ Change debugging
@endmindmap
